> I couldn't see any change regarding exposing partitions in MessageRouter.java file? I couldn't fully understand the change. can you provide a usecase for it?

@rdhabalia 

the partitions now is exposed at `TopicMetadata`, which is available at `#choosePartitions(msg, topicMetadata)`.

an example of customized message router would be : 

```
class SequenceIdMessageRouter implements MessageRouter {

     public int choosePartition(Message msg, TopicMetadata metadata) {
          return msg.getSequenceId() % metadata.numPartitions(); 
    }

}
```
